      "rendered": "The Top 10 Posts on Nonprofit Tech for Good in 2023"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>The top 10 posts on Nonprofit Tech for Good in 2023 reflect the trends that nonprofits were most interested in this past year.</p>\n<p>Social media still dominates the list as it has every year for the last decade. AI made a strong showing in 2023, and email marketing best practices are still in high demand.</p>\n<p>Thank you for being a part of the Nonprofit Tech for Good community in 2023. <strong>Enjoy your holiday break and cheers to 2024!</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/10-instagram-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\">10 Instagram Best Practices for Nonprofits</a> (12,803 views)</p>\n<p><strong>2)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/04/02/12-ways-to-use-chatgpt-and-other-ai-tools-for-fundraising/\">12 Ways to Use ChatGPT &amp; AI for Fundraising</a> (12,328 views)</p>\n<p><strong>3)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/02/25/how-nonprofits-can-grow-their-following-on-social-media/\">How to Grow Your Following on Social Media</a> (11,204 views)</p>\n<p><strong>4)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/04/27/43-digital-marketing-tools-resources-for-nonprofits/\">43 Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising Tools</a> (9,529 views)</p>\n<p><strong>5)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/10-email-marketing-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\">10 Email Marketing Best Practices for Nonprofits</a> (9,353 views)</p>\n<p><strong>6)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/07/07/threads-for-nonprofits-5-tips-for-the-early-adoption-phase/\">Threads for Nonprofits: 5 Tips for Early Adoption</a> (8,519 views)</p>\n<p><strong>7)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/06/19/14-job-boards-for-nonprofit-professionals-worldwide/\">14 Job Boards for Nonprofit Professionals Worldwide</a> (8,101 views)</p>\n<p><strong>8)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/08/04/6-generations-of-giving-who-gives-the-most-and-how-they-prefer-to-give/\">6 Generations of Giving: Who Gives the Most &amp; How</a> (7,881 views)</p>\n<p><strong>9)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/04/23/how-to-enhance-your-nonprofits-written-content-with-artificial-intelligence/\">How to Enhance Written Content with AI</a> (7,478 views)</p>\n<p><strong>10)</strong> <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/2023/06/24/a-guide-to-email-accessibility-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\">Email Accessibility Best Practices for Nonprofits</a> (6,340 views)</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Our <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Certificate in Social Media Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a> program covers the fundamentals of social media marketing and fundraising for your nonprofit. Participants will learn how to create a social media strategy, how to craft a content marketing plan, and current best practices for using social media for community engagement and fundraising.</p>\n<p>The program requires the completion of three webinars and costs $100 USD. To earn the 2024 certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both. <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Learn more &amp; register</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-41867 size-full aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2025-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Mrketing-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=900%2C707&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2025-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Mrketing-for-Nonprofits.png?w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2025-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Mrketing-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2025-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Mrketing-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C603&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2025-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Mrketing-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" /></a></p>\n",
